text: Cathedral of Saint Volodymyr the Great The Cathedral of Saint Volodymyr the Great (, ) in the 6th arrondissement of Paris, is the cathedral church of the Ukrainian Catholic Eparchy of Saint Wladimir-Le-Grand de Paris in France. The eparchial bishop of the eparchy has been Borys Gudziak since 2012. ==See also== *Catholic Church *Ukrainian Greek Catholic Church ==External links== * GCatholic.org information * home page of the cathedral Category:Ukrainian Catholic cathedrals Category:Eastern Catholic cathedrals in France Ukrainian Category:Buildings and structures in the 6th arrondissement of Paris Category:Cathedrals in Paris
